  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0ba4\u0bc0 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Couple killed in house fire",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A mother who was injured in a fire that broke out in a room on the ground floor of a two storey house in the Magammana area in Homagama has died today (26), police said.",
        "Kahathuduwa police said a father was killed and three others, including a six-year-old daughter, were injured in the blaze.",
        "According to hospital sources, the condition of 19-year-old daughter Kavindi Ranasinghe, who was admitted to the hospital, is critical.",
        "The mother and relatives of the deceased were in the adjoining house when the fire broke out and the eldest daughter who was with them came to the room to comb her hair.",
        "The fire broke out around 8pm when the deceased was staying in the basement of a two-storey house with his wife, eldest daughter (19) and six-year-old daughter.",
        "The fire was extinguished by the locals and the injured have been admitted to the Homagama Base Hospital for treatment, police said.",
        "Six people injured in the fire have been admitted to the Porlai Children's Hospital and three others to the Colombo National Hospital. A 47 - year - old man died on the spot, police said."
      ],
